    > **question:** I‚Äôm a little confused by the description & setup of this test. Are we actually testing what the description says?
    > 
    > > when `hasSeatLinkData` is `true`
    > 
    > ```ruby
    > factory({ /*‚Ä¶*/ hasSeatLinkData: false})
